item.title: Speed and Usability Performance of Top UAE Websites.
item.description: Google recently pusblished a new version of their PageSpeed API. I wanted to play around with it a bit. So, I decided to build a page that displays a visualization of the speed of some of the most popular UAE websites. I went to Alexa in order to gather the data about the most popular websites in the UAE. I also added a few sites that were not on Alexa’s list.
